message.content:
I need to identify the capital contributed by shareholders in exchange for shares from the balance sheet.

Looking at the balance sheet, the line item that represents capital contributed by shareholders is "Paid-in Capital". This account shows the amount of money that shareholders have invested in the company in exchange for shares.

From the balance sheet:
- The initial amount of Paid-in Capital was 13,000,000.00 on 2023-12-31
- The ending amount of Paid-in Capital was 13,000,000.00 on 2024-02-05

The value remained the same during this period, indicating that no additional capital was contributed and no capital was returned to shareholders.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '13000000.00', 'end value': '13000000.00'}}
```
